# Spindle thresholds

## Individual-level profiles

The above plots pool values from different individuals.  To study
between-person differences better, we'll generate topo-plots
per-individual, for two metrics: spindle density and frequency.
(Note that the following plots do not have standardized
_z_-axes (heat/color) between different individuals.)

